v_sal constant number:= 20
v_name varchar2(100) not null

q'(father's day)'-- alternative quote operator


LOB(Large Object) used to store large amount of data--- 4 GB
LOB types--
CLOB- Character
BLOB-- Binary
BFILE-- Binary File
NCLOB-- National Language Character


Bind variables-- also called host variables

&-- substitution variable
'&name'-- character based value


group functions and decode can not be used with PLSQL objects.


Sequence--
create sequence
increment by
start with
nomaxvalue


outer block cannot have access to refer variables in inner block
inner block has access to refer variable in outer block
